<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 yī lì shí zi luò rù xié zhōng, nǐ ruò bù lǐ cǎi jiù dān wù nǐ qián xíng.
 yī gè bù hǎo de yì niàn jìn rù nǐ xīn zhōng, nǐ ruò bù jù jué, jiù yǐng xiǎng shì fèng.
 shén de ér nǚ zǒng yào jǐng xǐng, duì sā dàn zǒng shuō bù, duì shén yào shùn cóng.
 zhè tiáo lù shàng wǒ men tóng gōng. bǐ cǐ xiāng zhù róng yào zhǔ míng.
 shēn shēn xiāng xìn zhǔ bì yǐn dǎo, dào tiān yá hǎi jiǎo yào jì zhù shí shí jǐng xǐng.</lyrics>
<title>shí shí jǐng xǐng 迦南966</title>
